    <h4>Basic Example</h4>
    <p>Pagination is a <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> HTML item that includes a nested HTML ordered list to display the breadcrumb items. The parent class is <code>.ter-breadcrumb</code>, which is used at the top level.</p>
    <p>Active menu items can be notated by using the <code>.is-active</code> class on the active list item.</p>
    <p>Separators are automatically added via CSS.</p>
